        "action": "Ban graphic anti-abortion images in public spaces",
        "additional_details": "Graphic images are distressing, especially for children and vulnerable people. The public should not be exposed to shocking material in shared spaces. This would balance free expression with public wellbeing.",
        "background": "Introduce laws banning graphic abortion images in public places like streets, near schools, and transport hubs, with enforcement powers for local authorities.",
